{"tid":2109563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"九西初選出線隊伍數目是待初選協調會議後決定","createTime":"2020-07-15T10:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T10:16:57.000Z","uid":171338,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1f229b77e25f2adf87a90d43a3e0996f291c2f","tid":2109563,"uid":171338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"//今日我與一眾抗爭派立法會參選人出席記者招待會，有網媒引述我已決定「依然會參加立法會選舉」，希望作以下澄清。<br />\n<br />\n根據協定機制，九龍西是以「初選、民調」雙軌進行協調，而初選出線隊伍數目亦是待初選協調會議後決定。<br />\n<br />\n昨日結果公布後我深受一眾抗爭派朋友所鼓舞，固然希望有機會與戰友一起行下去。縱使如此，我馮達浚承諾一切將以協調會議結果為準，最終參選意向將待協調結果公布後再定奪。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/317W4KP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F317W4KP.png&h=7cb6b271&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df26ffec705d1a3bb2ea0f29f5f9bca854df52a4","tid":2109563,"uid":171338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:07:13.000Z","msg":"唔好比人帶風向"},{"pid":"a7c38066a74be263ecb5d5b446a604320d9c5b60","tid":2109563,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:09:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0dfbd6cf91dedfb9d564bda5cf2cef06144c04a","tid":2109563,"uid":171338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bfea77dfc3a3ffb703de54d00cedb6b94c1112e","tid":2109563,"uid":171338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24de1b3d50fb18aefbf59e5714cf836584c24270","tid":2109563,"uid":171338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff0d387e9117c5c0238d62ce9d4f476f95e0e1a3","tid":2109563,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:15:51.000Z","msg":"推呢個！"},{"pid":"d6a886dd5bc2220ac2be030ee2b21ac87a1910f0","tid":2109563,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab0eeff71bfd72e2ca3b5810939b2a